<p><span class="anchor" id="p15"></span><span class="c5">وفي حديث النبي عليه السلام:</span> <span class="c2">«نصرت بالرعب»</span> <span class="c2">«٢»</span><a href="#p15" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p16"></span><span class="c4">[ظ]</span><a href="#p16" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
